name: Gather Community Plant #005 - Marcelo Pinel
description:
The Gather Community Plant Collection features works from HicEtNunc artists and their artistic renditions of the GatherArt plant. The plant signifies beginnings, growth, eco friendliness, and the concept of nurturing what we love.

Marcelo Pinel is the artist behind the CyberMysticGarden, which is a collection of colorful and powerful scenes. Their work focuses on societies of the past as well as the religions and beliefs that span across time and space.

Buying this plant directly funds the GatherArt Foundation & the artist who planted this CleanNFT.
